    <briefdescription>
<para>Static GATT Service structure. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Allows the user the declare static GATT Services with the aim of reducing the used RAM. The <ref refid="group__bt__gatt__server_1ga04c7887fb67107bd060dd023fd3186d5" kindref="member">BT_GATT_SERVICE_DEFINE</ref> macro can be used to statically define and register a service. </para>
